quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  3,46,"And he shall speak to people in his cradle and in his manhood, and shall be among the righteous"
  3,47,"She said, \"Lord! How can I have a son, when man has not yet touched me?\" He said, \"Thus Allah creates what He pleases. When He decrees a matter He only says: BE! And it is"
  3,48,"And He will teach him the Scripture and wisdom, and the Torah and the Gospel"
  3,49,"And he shall be a Messenger to the people of Israel (saying), \"Verily, I have come to you, with a sign from Allah, namely, that I will create for you out of clay a form of a bird, and I will blow thereon and it shall become a bird by Allah´s pe"
  3,50,"And I come confirming what was before you of the Torah, and to make lawful for you some of that which was forbidden unto you. I come to you with a sign from your Lord, so fear Allah and follow me"
  3,51,"Allah is my Lord, and your Lord, so worship Him: - this is the straight path"
  3,52,"And when Jesus perceived their unbelief, He said, \"Who will be my helpers in the cause of Allah?\" The disciples said, \"We will be Allah´s helpers. We believe in Allah, so bear you witness that we have surrendered (unto Him)"